{"tid":805467,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Die Hard 6 片名確定為「McClane」年老年輕主角故事雙線並行","createTime":"2018-09-04T00:03:19.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-04T04:07:48.000Z","uid":41343,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b441ee7f7d9ca4e1416e2c53d1eeed0d017c54f6","tid":805467,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T00:03:19.000Z","msg":"The next installment of the Die Hard movies has a new title &mdash; and it&rsquo;s not Die Hard: Year One. Instead, what will now be the sixth release from the franchise surrounding Bruce Willis&lsquo; John McClane will be known as simply McClane, EW has confirmed.<br />\n<br />\nProducer Lorenzo di Bonaventura initially revealed the news in an interview with Empire magazine. &ldquo;You can tell our intention by the fact that the title page we handed in [for the script] says, McClane,&rdquo; he said. &ldquo;We want you to get invested in John McClane more than ever before.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nDi Bonaventura also confirmed what Willis previously said in 2015 about the next chapter, that the story will &ldquo;bounce back and forth&rdquo; between present-day McClane and a younger McClane. &ldquo;I don&rsquo;t know how you do Die Hard without Bruce,&rdquo; di Bonaventura said. &ldquo;The idea that he&rsquo;s not very significant in this movie is not accurate at all. We are gonna explore John McClane in his 20s. But just as prominent is the 60-year-old version.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\nDie Hard: Year One was an earlier title treatment given to the project around the time Len Wiseman, the director behind Live Free or Die Hard, had first been in negotiations to direct.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://ew.com/movies/2018/09/03/die-hard-6-title-mcclane/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Few.com%2Fmovies%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2Fdie-hard-6-title-mcclane%2F&d=fz5i0KtlmVA4Ty3kmwqQhcmDuOf2Rd%2FwnGcLKIjXoko%3D&h=ff9ae488\" target=\"_blank\">https://ew.com/movies/2018/09/03/die-hard-6-title-mcclane/</a>"},{"pid":"ce7abfd5147f3a63381b087ecc257f2facf3641b","tid":805467,"uid":13653,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T00:04:25.000Z","msg":"Logan"},{"pid":"3186493d81a0eedecac4f0b2df0fe81caf521e88","tid":805467,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ce7abfd5147f3a63381b087ecc257f2facf3641b","tid":805467,"uid":13653,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T00:04:25.000Z","msg":"Logan"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T00:06:20.000Z","msg":"Rambo"},{"pid":"12f2a05b775d5ee4e95bc0077c23f0197dc25c39","tid":805467,"uid":33104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T00:12:47.000Z","msg":"放過以個系列啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0a7a73858e19d25e6bd25289ac94cadfc3bd519","tid":805467,"uid":30762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T00:15:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resizing.flixster.com/yG8R1IgzaPmTlWcOAVhmJU2ogMg=/206x305/v1.bTsxMTE2ODE4NDtqOzE3ODU5OzEyMDA7ODAwOzEyMDA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresizing.flixster.com%2FyG8R1IgzaPmTlWcOAVhmJU2ogMg%3D%2F206x305%2Fv1.bTsxMTE2ODE4NDtqOzE3ODU5OzEyMDA7ODAwOzEyMDA&h=e9988c93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又拍多套？"},{"pid":"67667b7e8570b46eaa745fcbe31faa8cfb1c780b","tid":805467,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b0a7a73858e19d25e6bd25289ac94cadfc3bd519","tid":805467,"uid":30762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T00:15:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://resizing.flixster.com/yG8R1IgzaPmTlWcOAVhmJU2ogMg=/206x305/v1.bTsxMTE2ODE4NDtqOzE3ODU5OzEyMDA7ODAwOzEyMDA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fresizing.flixster.com%2FyG8R1IgzaPmTlWcOAVhmJU2ogMg%3D%2F206x305%2Fv1.bTsxMTE2ODE4NDtqOzE3ODU5OzEyMDA7ODAwOzEyMDA&h=e9988c93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又拍多套？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T00:16:14.000Z","msg":"Last Jedi 大導演"},{"pid":"e1e